  <summary date="2021-08-21T17:29:57Z" status="Introduced in House">Coronavirus Provider Protection Act

This bill generally exempts health care professionals and related health care entities (e.g., hospitals and medical clinics) from liability for harm caused in the course of arranging or providing health care services during the COVID-19 public health emergency.</summary>
